WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 8]

01:15.240 --> 01:16.010
Spirit Slay!

01:33.270 --> 01:35.780
Xiuyuan! Xiuyuan! Xiuyuan!

01:43.640 --> 01:45.220
The suicide-for-all spell.

01:45.880 --> 01:47.810
I underestimated you.

01:48.470 --> 01:49.500
The spirit energy can't flow through.

01:54.880 --> 01:57.620
His spirit meridians are broken with critical internal wounds.

01:58.110 --> 02:00.940
The Divine Tree is his only hope to live.

02:01.160 --> 02:01.940
Nonsense!

02:02.360 --> 02:03.420
You're the one who's doomed!

02:05.080 --> 02:06.090
Worthless trash,

02:06.640 --> 02:08.580
die together.

02:22.200 --> 02:22.940
Lifei, are you alright?

02:24.710 --> 02:25.460
Take care of Xiuyuan.

02:26.150 --> 02:27.500
Since you beg for death,

02:28.390 --> 02:29.530
I shall oblige.

02:36.240 --> 02:37.900
Five Elements Merge, Demon-Subduing.

04:22.030 --> 04:23.060
Pointless struggle.

04:23.830 --> 04:26.770
Villain, Mr. Zuo Qiu won't spare you!

04:28.960 --> 04:30.690
When I find the Divine Tree,

04:31.030 --> 04:32.660
I'll fear no one!

04:54.760 --> 04:56.370
Such surging spirit energy.

05:09.520 --> 05:10.450
Finally, you revealed yourself.

05:11.000 --> 05:12.890
If you'd been any later, we'd have been dead.

05:13.150 --> 05:14.210
My wounds haven't fully healed,

05:14.350 --> 05:15.540
yet I had to save you.

05:15.880 --> 05:17.300
Do you know how much cultivation I lost?

05:17.880 --> 05:18.420
I'm going to rest.

05:18.830 --> 05:19.980
Don't come to me in a year or half.

05:20.590 --> 05:22.210
Wait, please save Xiuyuan!

05:22.710 --> 05:24.450
His meridians are shattered, and his spirit root is ruined.

05:24.880 --> 05:25.500
There's nothing I can do.

05:25.830 --> 05:26.770
Let fate take its course.

05:27.590 --> 05:28.500
What?

05:29.230 --> 05:31.060
No, he mustn't die!

05:31.390 --> 05:32.130
Save him.

05:32.910 --> 05:34.770
Save him, please.

05:36.000 --> 05:36.740
Head to Qingqiu.

05:37.200 --> 05:39.180
The Ganhua Realm holds what can heal him.

05:39.830 --> 05:40.690
Qingqiu?

05:41.590 --> 05:42.060
Wait.

05:43.710 --> 05:44.370
Where

05:44.880 --> 05:46.980
is the Ganhua Realm, Riyan?

05:52.470 --> 05:53.250
You mustn't die!

05:55.000 --> 05:55.740
I'll save you.

06:02.710 --> 06:04.100
Xiuyuan! Xiuyuan!

06:06.640 --> 06:07.210
- Lifei? - Lifei?

06:08.760 --> 06:09.300
Xiuyuan.

06:11.080 --> 06:11.660
What's wrong with him?

06:13.390 --> 06:14.100
Let's hurry back to the academy.

06:16.150 --> 06:17.130
Don't bother.

06:19.150 --> 06:19.810
Mr. Hu.

06:20.440 --> 06:21.420
Find a place to bury him.

06:22.880 --> 06:23.620
If you won't save him, I will!

06:25.390 --> 06:27.130
Head back to Qingqiu. I have a way to heal him.

06:27.150 --> 06:28.420
I'm coming with you. Go.

06:29.000 --> 06:31.330
Mr. Hu, Xiuyuan is on the brink of death.

06:32.200 --> 06:33.620
We'll take him to Qingqiu.

06:34.230 --> 06:35.500
Once things calm down,

06:35.830 --> 06:37.250
we'll go to the academy to plead guilty.

06:37.680 --> 06:38.620
We beg for your permission.

06:42.120 --> 06:43.420
One's fate is predetermined.

06:45.560 --> 06:47.010
What if you fail to save him?

06:48.230 --> 06:49.010
As his fellow disciples,

06:49.270 --> 06:51.330
we should stand together through hardship and do our best.

06:52.080 --> 06:53.740
If we get expelled from the academy for this,

06:54.200 --> 06:55.250
we'll accept it without regret.

06:56.030 --> 06:56.500
Yes.

06:57.790 --> 06:58.330
That's right.

07:08.150 --> 07:08.660
Xiuyuan!

07:08.760 --> 07:09.180
Xiuyuan!

07:09.790 --> 07:10.570
What are you doing?

07:13.910 --> 07:16.740
Lifei, Mr. Hu is saving him.

07:22.120 --> 07:23.690
I've stabilized his heart meridians for now.

07:24.390 --> 07:26.180
He won‘t be dead in at least three stays,

07:27.150 --> 07:29.890
but what happens later depends on his fate.

07:31.030 --> 07:33.100
I'll cover for you with the academy.

07:33.520 --> 07:35.770
Bring him back safe once you cure him.

07:36.470 --> 07:39.010
You're too young to stay outside alone.

07:44.270 --> 07:45.500
What does he mean?

07:46.200 --> 07:47.660
Is he going to cover for us?

07:48.150 --> 07:49.860
Never mind. Save Xiuyuan first.

07:53.590 --> 07:54.100
Let's go.

08:13.270 --> 08:13.890
Your Highness,

08:14.350 --> 08:15.890
your cultivation is astonishing now.

08:16.320 --> 08:17.330
Like our teachers,

08:17.880 --> 08:19.450
you can weave a spirit energy barrier for healing.

08:20.350 --> 08:21.540
The Zhurong Stone is powerful.

08:22.000 --> 08:23.690
It can sustain spirit energy,

08:24.120 --> 08:25.500
barely enough to last for a few hours.

08:26.590 --> 08:29.060
A few hours? Exactly how long?

08:29.150 --> 08:29.890
Don't worry.

08:31.230 --> 08:32.500
Xiuyuan is out of immediate danger.

08:33.270 --> 08:34.180
Stay here and look after him.

08:34.760 --> 08:36.420
We'll search for the Ganhua Realm.

08:37.280 --> 08:38.090
I can search.

08:39.540 --> 08:41.810
Lifei, your spirit power is faint,

08:42.110 --> 08:43.730
and you've channeled energy to Xiuyuan nonstop.

08:44.230 --> 08:45.660
You can barely stand right now.

08:45.960 --> 08:46.570
Yeah.

08:46.960 --> 08:48.660
There's plenty of medicinal herbs here.

08:49.280 --> 08:51.330
Lifei, boil some nourishing medicine.

08:51.470 --> 08:52.380
We'll be back soon.

08:55.200 --> 08:57.210
Qingqiu's mountains are steep, filled with spirits,

08:57.590 --> 08:58.730
but most mean no harm.

08:59.110 --> 09:00.540
If you run into trouble,

09:01.230 --> 09:02.690
tell them you're Xiaobangchui's friends.

09:03.280 --> 09:03.810
Stay safe.

09:05.110 --> 09:05.540
Okay.

09:22.800 --> 09:24.730
When my master and I traveled,

09:25.320 --> 09:28.090
we lodged in inns with money, and shrines without.

09:29.660 --> 09:31.260
After coming back to Qingqiu,

09:33.280 --> 09:34.940
we spent two to three months

09:35.040 --> 09:36.690
rebuilding this wooden house.

09:37.540 --> 09:39.020
This is our only home.

09:39.040 --> 09:40.300
No outsiders have set foot here.

09:41.230 --> 09:42.810
You're our first visitor,

09:43.230 --> 09:45.940
but look at you, bedridden as soon as you arrived.

10:01.590 --> 10:02.730
Are you crazy?

10:03.630 --> 10:05.570
Why risk your life saving me time and again?

10:15.710 --> 10:16.780
Giving up saving your brother?

10:20.470 --> 10:21.940
Why treat me so well?

10:42.350 --> 10:45.660
My master said never owe anyone a favor.

10:47.110 --> 10:49.570
I'll help rescue him

10:50.560 --> 10:52.380
once you recover, okay?

11:05.940 --> 11:06.610
Found nothing?

11:08.830 --> 11:10.540
We searched every spirit spot

11:10.560 --> 11:11.180
across Qingqiu,

11:11.750 --> 11:13.730
yet sensed no spot with strange spirit energy.

11:15.630 --> 11:18.180
Lifei, living here ages,

11:18.630 --> 11:19.940
don't you know the Ganhua Realm?

11:24.220 --> 11:25.260
Who told you about it?

11:26.100 --> 11:27.330
Does the Ganhua Realm truly exist?

11:31.940 --> 11:32.780
Say something!

11:37.110 --> 11:37.940
As a hidden secret realm,

11:38.220 --> 11:39.140
it can't be easily

11:39.180 --> 11:40.090
tracked down.

11:42.680 --> 11:44.730
It's fine. I'll search tomorrow morning again.

11:46.180 --> 11:47.210
But Mr. Hu warned

11:47.990 --> 11:49.140
that Xiuyuan only has three days to live.

11:49.470 --> 11:51.180
A day and a half have passed, and you...

11:54.940 --> 11:55.490
Xiuyuan!

11:56.560 --> 11:57.060
Xiuyuan!

12:16.710 --> 12:17.610
I'm going out to search now.

12:19.590 --> 12:20.140
Lifei.

12:35.350 --> 12:37.380
None of you know where the Ganhua Realm is?

12:39.830 --> 12:40.450
Wait.

12:53.160 --> 12:53.970
Tell

12:53.990 --> 12:55.780
every spirit and monster you can find

12:56.110 --> 12:57.380
that I'll offer anything

13:00.040 --> 13:01.140
in exchange for clues.

13:09.870 --> 13:10.450
Lifei.

13:14.110 --> 13:15.260
Your spirit power is long exhausted.

13:15.710 --> 13:17.940
Keep this up, and you'll collapse next.

13:18.960 --> 13:19.660
Tongzhou,

13:20.510 --> 13:22.540
what if the Ganhua Realm isn't real?

13:25.960 --> 13:27.260
Who told you

13:28.110 --> 13:29.330
it can save Xiuyuan?

13:30.200 --> 13:32.260
My friend.

13:33.920 --> 13:36.730
But what if I misheard?

13:37.510 --> 13:38.850
What if we never find it?

13:39.470 --> 13:40.780
Will Xiuyuan die?

13:44.320 --> 13:45.300
We'll find it for sure.

13:46.230 --> 13:48.610
We can use herbs, channel spirit energy,

13:49.160 --> 13:50.490
and try every possible means

13:51.350 --> 13:52.020
to save him.

13:57.320 --> 13:58.690
You're just comforting me.

13:59.630 --> 14:00.300
I don't need empty words.

14:01.400 --> 14:02.260
Only one day left.

14:03.800 --> 14:04.610
I'll find it.

14:06.160 --> 14:07.810
I'll definitely locate the Ganhua Realm.

14:10.040 --> 14:10.610
Lifei.

14:25.680 --> 14:26.940
I picked some healing herbs

14:27.960 --> 14:29.090
for Xiuyuan.

14:37.280 --> 14:37.900
Changyue.

14:41.440 --> 14:42.060
Xiuyuan!

14:43.710 --> 14:44.330
Xiuyuan!

14:47.200 --> 14:48.260
His pulse is far too faint.

14:48.750 --> 14:49.850
He was supposed to last another day.

15:26.630 --> 15:27.970
I'll offer anything

15:29.560 --> 15:30.610
in exchange for clues.

15:34.960 --> 15:36.610
Those spirits crave my blood.

15:38.350 --> 15:40.940
Yeah. My blood might work.

15:49.350 --> 15:49.970
Drink it.

15:56.750 --> 15:59.020
Drink it.

15:59.870 --> 16:00.850
Drink it.

16:10.510 --> 16:11.140
Xiuyuan.

16:16.870 --> 16:20.210
Xiuyuan. Xiuyuan. Xiuyuan.

16:34.350 --> 16:36.850
Stay awake! Open your eyes!

16:55.470 --> 16:56.180
Lei Xiuyuan!

17:05.230 --> 17:06.180
This won't do.

17:06.440 --> 17:07.450
Is there any other way?

17:07.750 --> 17:09.250
Lifei. Lifei!

17:42.160 --> 17:44.580
Essence and Qi form the Core. Take the Inner Core out of the body...

17:45.640 --> 17:46.530
The Ten Forbidden Arts of Sorcerers.

17:48.270 --> 17:48.860
What's this?

17:51.440 --> 17:53.620
You can't just take your inner core out.

17:54.100 --> 17:54.770
To save him,

17:55.270 --> 17:56.730
you'd believe any crooked forbidden trick?

17:56.750 --> 17:57.620
Are you throwing your life away?

17:57.840 --> 17:59.180
You want to trade your life for Xiuyuan's,

17:59.710 --> 18:00.940
but he would never allow it.

18:05.790 --> 18:08.770
No matter what we try, nothing works.

18:09.750 --> 18:11.340
But the three days will be up soon.

18:12.100 --> 18:13.210
What can we do?

18:18.920 --> 18:20.100
Qingqiu swarms with spirits,

18:20.640 --> 18:21.940
so ordinary people cannot dwell here.

18:22.840 --> 18:24.770
Your master kept you safe here all these years,

18:25.200 --> 18:26.340
so he must be a hidden expert.

18:27.270 --> 18:28.770
Did he ever mention

18:29.400 --> 18:30.210
healing herbs

18:31.230 --> 18:32.210
or any special land?

18:33.550 --> 18:36.010
[Young Lifei]
Xiaobangchui, don't worry.

18:36.030 --> 18:37.730
I'll find a way to heal you.

18:43.510 --> 18:44.580
I remember now.

18:53.510 --> 18:54.580
It's right over there,

18:55.470 --> 18:56.860
but I can't recall the entrance.

18:57.160 --> 18:58.820
If the Ganhua Realm holds mysterious power,

18:59.100 --> 19:00.340
its terrain must carry clues.

19:01.030 --> 19:02.820
My master always said yin and yang coexist.

19:03.070 --> 19:04.770
The void is substance. Emptiness is fullness.

19:06.400 --> 19:06.900
Be careful.

19:11.840 --> 19:12.450
Let's check it down there.

19:19.840 --> 19:20.730
Stars?

19:23.510 --> 19:24.530
These look like islands.

19:25.790 --> 19:28.010
Legends say thousands of isles lie beyond the sea,

19:29.200 --> 19:31.140
yet there are far more here than that.

19:38.340 --> 19:39.450
Testing each one

19:40.200 --> 19:41.420
would take a whole day.

19:42.840 --> 19:44.970
Dawn draws near. Xiuyuan can't wait that long.

19:45.310 --> 19:46.050
Try them now.

20:08.510 --> 20:09.940
Lifei. Lifei.

20:10.510 --> 20:11.940
Let me do it, Lifei.

20:13.880 --> 20:14.580
Lifei.

21:11.100 --> 21:14.480
[Ganhua Realm]

21:43.920 --> 21:44.690
You see that?

21:45.680 --> 21:46.340
What?

21:46.600 --> 21:47.340
It lit up!

22:08.640 --> 22:09.450
I remembered.

22:10.840 --> 22:11.490
This is the one.

22:22.340 --> 22:23.770
I'll do it. Keep watch nearby.

22:48.750 --> 22:52.340
Such immense spirit power. Could it be this round stone?

23:00.900 --> 23:04.580
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

23:04.900 --> 23:06.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

23:06.200 --> 23:07.010
Hnag in there.

23:07.860 --> 23:11.180
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

23:11.420 --> 23:13.620
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

23:14.660 --> 23:18.140
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

23:18.860 --> 23:21.220
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

23:21.820 --> 23:23.340
♪No calamity can rival♪

23:23.740 --> 23:26.780
♪the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

23:28.920 --> 23:32.400
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

23:33.160 --> 23:35.400
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

23:35.840 --> 23:38.880
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

23:39.960 --> 23:40.730
This spirit power...

23:40.730 --> 23:41.800
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

23:42.600 --> 23:46.080
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

23:46.440 --> 23:48.720
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

23:49.240 --> 23:52.200
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign♪

23:52.920 --> 23:55.120
♪Supreme♪

23:56.200 --> 23:59.730
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

24:00.400 --> 24:02.770
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

24:03.090 --> 24:06.290
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds, break through the waves♪

24:06.890 --> 24:09.170
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

24:09.570 --> 24:13.290
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

24:13.930 --> 24:16.330
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

24:16.770 --> 24:19.930
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

24:20.530 --> 24:22.890
♪And falling petals♪

24:23.610 --> 24:27.880
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

24:32.030 --> 24:32.620
Lifei.

24:33.440 --> 24:34.010
Xiuyuan.

24:58.160 --> 24:58.900
Xiuyuan.

25:01.230 --> 25:03.340
You're awake, Lifei.

25:06.230 --> 25:08.210
What about Xiuyuan? Is he alright?

25:08.710 --> 25:10.290
He's safe.

25:10.640 --> 25:11.290
Calm down.

25:11.510 --> 25:12.490
You've been asleep for three days.

25:13.270 --> 25:14.100
Three days?

25:15.160 --> 25:16.420
Xiuyuan, be careful.

25:34.310 --> 25:35.100
Xiuyuan!

25:45.750 --> 25:48.710
♪When fate calls, I rise as a worthy one♪

25:48.830 --> 25:51.470
♪I'll never back down♪

25:51.510 --> 25:57.010
♪I keep my former fearless resolve, never return it♪

25:57.730 --> 26:01.490
♪Dusk till dawn, I stay awake♪

26:01.610 --> 26:04.570
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

26:05.840 --> 26:06.730
Is it really healed?

26:07.310 --> 26:08.250
Are you fully recovered?

26:08.710 --> 26:11.180
Yes, I've checked thoroughly.

26:11.640 --> 26:12.620
His broken meridians are reconnected.

26:13.120 --> 26:15.180
The Ganhua Realm is truly a miraculous place.

26:16.030 --> 26:18.940
That's just wonderful.

26:18.940 --> 26:21.200
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

26:21.200 --> 26:22.100
You have no idea

26:22.750 --> 26:24.250
how badly you were hurt.

26:25.710 --> 26:26.530
Never use

26:27.550 --> 26:28.940
that suicide-for-all spell again,

26:29.230 --> 26:30.290
you hear me?

26:30.510 --> 26:31.820
I was terrified.

26:41.680 --> 26:42.380
I won't.

26:44.310 --> 26:46.530
You... You'd better keep your word.

26:47.340 --> 26:48.250
If you try it again,

26:49.510 --> 26:50.180
I...

26:51.330 --> 26:53.930
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

26:54.130 --> 26:58.730
♪The hidden fire in my heart forges a massive sword♪

26:59.010 --> 27:03.410
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

27:03.410 --> 27:05.470
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

27:05.470 --> 27:07.580
Promise you'll never sacrifice yourself for me.

27:07.580 --> 27:11.330
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

27:11.680 --> 27:15.560
♪Climb high, lone sword sings, dance beneath autumn moon♪

27:15.760 --> 27:17.920
♪Dreams wane, then bloom full soon♪

27:18.080 --> 27:23.680
♪Rough the road, yet my steps shall never cease to move♪

27:24.060 --> 27:27.680
♪Banners wave, war drums thunder across the sky♪

27:27.800 --> 27:30.110
♪I tread fleeting mist beneath my feet♪

27:30.280 --> 27:36.000
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

27:39.510 --> 27:40.690
Alright.

27:43.340 --> 27:45.180
Survive hardship, and good luck awaits.

27:47.790 --> 27:49.620
Here, a bowl each.

27:50.200 --> 27:51.050
Cry after drinking.

27:52.680 --> 27:53.250
True that.

27:53.470 --> 27:55.210
Survive hardship, and good luck awaits. Here.

27:57.160 --> 27:57.820
A bowl each.

27:59.400 --> 27:59.970
Drink it all.

29:58.640 --> 30:00.250
The strange spirit aura of the tower.

30:02.920 --> 30:03.620
The Divine Tree.

30:07.550 --> 30:08.660
You know, over there.

30:09.030 --> 30:10.660
The mushrooms there are the best.

30:11.120 --> 30:12.140
I gather them

30:12.270 --> 30:13.660
after every rain.

30:14.230 --> 30:16.820
Sometimes, I caught rabbits

30:17.400 --> 30:19.530
to stew with mushrooms.

30:23.310 --> 30:24.530
Qingqiu is such a nice land.

30:26.310 --> 30:27.250
Do you like it?

30:30.360 --> 30:31.770
Then live here together with me.

30:39.270 --> 30:40.970
To... together?

30:43.030 --> 30:43.690
Look.

30:43.840 --> 30:45.660
You said your wish

30:45.680 --> 30:47.140
is to live peacefully with your brother.

30:47.600 --> 30:49.100
Qingqiu is such a vast land.

30:49.710 --> 30:51.580
Once you rescue him

30:51.990 --> 30:53.010
and I find my master,

30:53.360 --> 30:54.690
we can come back together.

30:55.440 --> 30:56.140
Then

30:57.600 --> 30:58.250
we'll build

30:58.990 --> 31:00.250
a house right there

31:00.550 --> 31:03.690
and grow radishes in the yard.

31:38.750 --> 31:41.210
Hey, let me introduce.

31:41.470 --> 31:44.380
This is Lei Xiuyuan, my best friend.

31:53.550 --> 31:55.140
Your surging spirit energy

31:55.360 --> 31:56.250
has intimidated them.

31:56.990 --> 31:57.340
I...

31:58.200 --> 32:00.940
Don't be scared.

32:01.310 --> 32:02.970
He is one of us.

32:29.470 --> 32:30.900
Qingqiu swarms with bugs and mosquitoes.

32:30.990 --> 32:32.100
They grow more venomous as autumn comes.

32:32.840 --> 32:34.970
Smoke the room, and you'll sleep soundly tonight.

32:39.470 --> 32:40.100
Are you alright?

32:40.680 --> 32:41.180
I'm fine.

32:43.990 --> 32:45.820
This is my master's treasure chest.

32:57.750 --> 32:59.100
Records of Overseas Legends.

33:00.960 --> 33:02.900
You can read these weird characters?

33:03.880 --> 33:06.180
I snuck peeks before, but couldn't understand.

33:10.120 --> 33:11.770
How did I learn these characters?

33:20.750 --> 33:21.490
What's this?

33:25.360 --> 33:27.690
Mostly about legends of overseas lands.

33:30.160 --> 33:32.860
Beyond the East Sea's Ruins live exotic monster clans,

33:33.550 --> 33:36.380
their skin pitch-black and two serpents coiled in their hands.

33:38.270 --> 33:39.450
How incredible.

33:42.400 --> 33:45.050
Could my master have planned to live overseas?

33:48.030 --> 33:48.970
As a sorcerer,

33:49.960 --> 33:52.340
he lived safely in spirit-infested Qingqiu,

33:53.600 --> 33:56.180
while hiding from the world, concealing his identity,

33:56.640 --> 33:57.770
and knowing all about overseas lands.

33:59.310 --> 33:59.970
Who exactly

34:01.310 --> 34:02.250
is he?

34:06.990 --> 34:08.420
The Mid-autumn Festival is almost here.

34:08.550 --> 34:10.180
Why hasn't Tongzhou come back yet?

34:11.920 --> 34:12.940
Our teacher told you

34:13.440 --> 34:15.450
that Mr. Zuo sent him to visit a master.

34:16.190 --> 34:16.740
In this world,

34:16.760 --> 34:18.570
there can't be many masters

34:18.590 --> 34:19.610
stronger than Mr. Xuanshan.

34:20.110 --> 34:22.050
Besides, why can Lifei go,

34:22.070 --> 34:23.300
but I'm not allowed to go along?

34:24.320 --> 34:24.900
Well...

34:26.880 --> 34:28.090
Youran,

34:29.760 --> 34:30.780
do you know

34:30.800 --> 34:31.740
when Tongzhou will return?

34:32.720 --> 34:35.450
The master thought they were outstanding talents,

34:35.470 --> 34:36.570
so they kept them for a few extra days.

34:38.150 --> 34:40.490
A master? What master?

34:40.670 --> 34:42.420
What's their name? Which sect do they belong to?

34:43.360 --> 34:45.490
A true master's identity is never to be revealed.

34:47.400 --> 34:48.050
Master.

34:50.440 --> 34:53.090
This chicken is acting weird today.

34:54.030 --> 34:56.450
If you don't tell me the truth,

34:56.510 --> 34:58.050
I'll pluck all its feathers out.

34:58.070 --> 34:59.940
Wait. Don't be rash!

34:59.990 --> 35:01.010
Calm down, please!

35:01.030 --> 35:02.010
Don't act recklessly.

35:02.030 --> 35:03.220
Calm down?

35:03.940 --> 35:05.170
I'm really going to pluck it.

35:05.720 --> 35:06.220
Your Ladyship.

35:07.070 --> 35:07.570
Your Ladyship.

35:08.820 --> 35:09.490
Your Ladyship.

35:09.900 --> 35:11.490
It bit me!

35:11.510 --> 35:11.970
Your Ladyship.

35:11.990 --> 35:14.090
A mere chicken dares to attack me!

35:14.720 --> 35:16.260
I told you to calm down.

35:17.630 --> 35:19.130
So young yet so fiery,

35:19.420 --> 35:20.570
you may not grow taller.

35:21.460 --> 35:22.300
Are you alright?

35:23.240 --> 35:24.010
Lifei, let me handle this.

35:24.670 --> 35:25.300
Be careful.

35:27.190 --> 35:28.010
Come on, let's eat.

35:28.820 --> 35:30.970
I'll show you my signature dishes.

35:31.420 --> 35:34.050
This is Nectar Radish Soup.

35:34.900 --> 35:35.650
This exquisite carving

35:36.720 --> 35:39.530
is Fortune Rolling Radish.

35:41.240 --> 35:42.570
When I have time, I'll make my ultimate specialty

35:42.860 --> 35:45.340
that goes perfectly with three steamed buns at a go.

35:45.780 --> 35:46.420
What?

35:46.630 --> 35:47.300
What's that?

35:47.990 --> 35:48.700
What is it?

35:49.550 --> 35:51.220
Marinated radish and soy pickled radish.

35:56.470 --> 35:58.220
Now I get why your master

35:58.240 --> 35:59.610
called you Xiaobangchui.

35:59.940 --> 36:02.050
These radishes look just like mallets, which represent your previous name.

36:02.510 --> 36:04.570
No, my master called me Xiaobangchui

36:04.980 --> 36:06.740
because when he found me by the river,

36:06.780 --> 36:08.130
a young woman was beating clothes

36:08.510 --> 36:09.780
with a wooden mallet.

36:09.820 --> 36:11.090
She was breathtakingly beautiful.

36:11.470 --> 36:12.610
My master wanted to remember her,

36:12.630 --> 36:13.860
so he called me Xiaobangchui.

36:16.670 --> 36:17.420
That story fits well.

36:29.470 --> 36:31.650
Lifei, do you have any other kin?

36:32.300 --> 36:34.450
I do, six of them.

36:35.070 --> 36:36.130
Where are they?

36:37.030 --> 36:39.260
One is my senior brother, whom I've never met.

36:39.550 --> 36:40.970
I have no clue where he is.

36:42.300 --> 36:43.490
As for the other five,

36:43.630 --> 36:44.740
they're right here with me.

37:00.300 --> 37:01.380
My master once said

37:01.550 --> 37:03.530
that in the restless world, people are unfeeling.

37:03.900 --> 37:05.450
Most only chase luck and flee misfortune.

37:06.110 --> 37:08.860
A person who treats you faithfully amid hardship

37:09.030 --> 37:11.170
and stands by you unto death surpasses your family.

37:15.030 --> 37:15.780
Lifei is right.

37:16.780 --> 37:17.970
From this day on,

37:18.300 --> 37:20.420
we're like family, bound as siblings.

37:20.670 --> 37:21.970
Yes, family.

37:29.720 --> 37:30.820
Since we're family,

37:31.340 --> 37:35.300
I have a truth to confess to you today.

37:57.150 --> 38:00.970
I am the Crown Prince of Gaolu,

38:02.550 --> 38:05.260
whom Zong Quan has long sought to wipe out entirely.

38:21.550 --> 38:22.420
Over the years,

38:24.110 --> 38:24.940
Xiuyuan has endured

38:26.190 --> 38:27.380
all the suffering for me.

38:35.470 --> 38:37.650
States across the Central Plains have waged wars for a hundred years.

38:38.240 --> 38:39.450
For every key imperial heir,

38:39.980 --> 38:41.090
a child of the same age

38:41.460 --> 38:43.090
is arranged from childhood

38:43.110 --> 38:43.820
as their body double.

38:45.190 --> 38:47.650
Xiuyuan must be Ye Ye's double.

38:53.340 --> 38:54.170
No blame falls on Ye Ye.

38:55.340 --> 38:57.610
Such imperial secrets are hard to speak aloud.

38:58.990 --> 39:00.260
Yet Xiuyuan bore the harder lot.

39:00.860 --> 39:03.170
Facing death time and again, he never revealed his true identity.

39:06.940 --> 39:08.650
Xiuyuan, I‘m sorry.

39:09.070 --> 39:10.340
Had I told the truth earlier,

39:10.720 --> 39:12.420
Zong Quan wouldn't have hunted you relentlessly.

39:12.470 --> 39:12.900
I...

39:12.940 --> 39:15.740
What he's done has nothing to do with you.

39:27.030 --> 39:27.610
Ye Ye,

39:29.820 --> 39:30.900
we have survived all the horrors,

39:32.460 --> 39:34.700
so let's not dwell on the past.

39:35.240 --> 39:35.900
Xiuyuan.

39:36.240 --> 39:39.340
We've grown up, and we're all still alive.

39:40.670 --> 39:41.420
That is enough.

39:43.150 --> 39:45.220
You're right, no more looking back.

39:45.460 --> 39:46.530
We must march forward.

39:46.990 --> 39:47.650
Look at us now.

39:47.980 --> 39:49.650
We're all here together like a family.

39:49.670 --> 39:51.050
We have food to eat and a school to attend.

39:52.110 --> 39:52.970
Dig in, quick!

39:52.990 --> 39:54.860
My radish soup has gone cold. Come on.

39:58.380 --> 39:58.820
This

40:00.240 --> 40:01.940
God of Wealth statue is definitely for Tongzhou.

40:08.190 --> 40:08.780
Alright.

40:09.150 --> 40:10.940
If you ask of me, whatever I possess,

40:11.380 --> 40:12.300
I'll give every last bit to you.

40:14.380 --> 40:16.220
No surprise they call you cash...

40:21.550 --> 40:22.420
A walking God of Wealth.

40:25.860 --> 40:26.380
Wait.

40:27.990 --> 40:30.050
Did you see me as a cash cow from the very start?

40:30.670 --> 40:31.610
Never!

40:32.460 --> 40:34.570
I've always treated Your Highness with sincerity.

40:40.340 --> 40:41.220
Eat more, go on.

40:41.860 --> 40:42.970
Try this dish.

40:43.300 --> 40:44.970
Lifei, you're truly skilled at cooking.

40:44.990 --> 40:46.300
- Here. - This radish tastes incredible.

40:46.340 --> 40:47.940
- Xiuyuan. Have a bowl of soup first. - So tasty.

40:48.380 --> 40:50.450
This one's delicious too, Changyue.

40:50.780 --> 40:52.170
Tongzhou, let me serve you another bowl.

40:52.420 --> 40:53.010
Have some too.

40:57.470 --> 40:59.260
Only the power of a fox spirit can save him.

41:00.110 --> 41:01.340
The sooner you catch the fox spirit,

41:01.550 --> 41:03.220
the sooner you'll see Mr. Lu.

41:03.980 --> 41:06.050
A person who treats you faithfully amid hardship

41:06.420 --> 41:08.820
and stands by you unto death surpasses your family.

41:09.190 --> 41:09.860
Right.

41:10.510 --> 41:13.340
From this day on, we are family.

41:21.340 --> 41:21.970
Xiuyuan.

41:23.550 --> 41:24.260
Xiuyuan!

41:27.470 --> 41:27.970
Look here.

41:28.780 --> 41:31.220
Listen, this rabbit stole my radishes.

41:31.340 --> 41:32.490
I tricked it down at last.

41:32.860 --> 41:34.780
Steal again, and I'll stew you with radishes!

41:42.380 --> 41:44.450
I just called you several times, and you didn't answer.

41:45.860 --> 41:46.970
Got something on your mind?

42:42.200 --> 42:42.450
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.450 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel,
The Eternal Fragrance]

42:54.620 --> 42:57.900
♪Nightmares rage before the dawn♪

42:58.020 --> 43:01.540
♪Merely ephemeral blooms that fade in a blink♪

43:01.740 --> 43:06.740
♪Crushed ten thousand times, yet we embrace the pain♪

43:06.940 --> 43:10.580
♪Heaven sent us here, no ordinary youths♪

43:10.740 --> 43:13.860
♪Through calamities, we do not hold back♪

43:14.020 --> 43:20.140
♪With righteous faith, we seal away the perils of the world♪

43:21.060 --> 43:25.420
♪All the way from the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

43:25.700 --> 43:28.340
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

43:28.500 --> 43:31.540
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

43:31.620 --> 43:34.820
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

43:34.940 --> 43:38.060
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

43:38.220 --> 43:41.100
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

43:41.140 --> 43:44.260
♪One final battle, we charge ahead♪

43:44.340 --> 43:48.140
♪The path of light is not far away♪

